    "result": {"data":{"strapiPost":{"strapiId":3907,"title":"One Way To The South","topic":"Travel","slug":"one-way-to-the-south","coverImage":{"publicURL":"/static/d5d5318b41ca49e55fa65556660bfca3/f3920ff6c9a5aef557bdeb3b482ec4d8.jpg"},"photoCredit":"Allegiant","date":"2021-11-19","content":"<p>The <a href=\"https://www.flyxna.com/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Arkansas National Airport</a> (XNA) is launching 2 new non-stop routes this week, adding to the list of winter holiday trip opportunities.&nbsp;</p><ul><li><strong>Lift off:</strong> The inaugural flight to Punta Gorda Airport (PGD) in Florida is <a href=\"https://www.nwahomepage.com/news/allegiant-airlines-unveils-two-new-non-stop-routes-out-of-xna-this-week/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">today</a>, locking in the <a href=\"https://fareflightnwa.org/xna-has-8-florida-routes-but-lets-explore-which-one-is-best/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">8th</a> direct flight from XNA to Florida. <a href=\"https://www.nwahomepage.com/news/allegiant-airlines-unveils-two-new-non-stop-routes-out-of-xna-this-week/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Friday</a> will be the initiation of&nbsp;William P. Hobby Airport (HOU) in Houston, Texas as a destination from XNA. The new flights will both operate twice a week.&nbsp;</li><li><strong>Non-stop:</strong> The non-stop flight to PGD is starting with one-way fares as low as <a href=\"https://talkbusiness.net/2021/11/xna-grows-to-27-nonstop-flights-with-start-of-new-allegiant-service/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">$43</a>, and the beginning one-way fares to HOU are as low as <a href=\"https://talkbusiness.net/2021/11/xna-grows-to-27-nonstop-flights-with-start-of-new-allegiant-service/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">$33</a>. After these new routes, XNA has a total of <a href=\"https://fareflightnwa.org/xna-has-8-florida-routes-but-lets-explore-which-one-is-best/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">27</a> non-stop flights.&nbsp;</li></ul><p>Learn more <a href=\"https://talkbusiness.net/2021/11/xna-grows-to-27-nonstop-flights-with-start-of-new-allegiant-service/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">HERE</a>.&nbsp;</p>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"one-way-to-the-south"}},
